{
  "texts": [
    "The extraction of multi-word aspects and opinions has received an improvement through notable models such as Span-ASTE [2] and span-level bidirectional methods [3].",
    "There is no extensive study available regarding equivalent approaches for extracting components from Bangla texts.",
    "Key ContributionsA novel ASTE model for Bangla represents our major proposal which includes creation of the first extensive ASTE dataset for Bangla through data collection from e-commerce sites like Daraz and social media channels Facebook and Rokomari.",
    "The proposed ASTE framework adopts specialized components which match aspects with opinions using graph techniques and semantic similarity methods for processing Bangla text.",
    "The model incorporates two models where sentiment classification is boosted with an ensemble system that combines XGBoost with BanglaBERT."
  ]
}